looking very
endomorphic…


![](figures/198.1)


... and after, looking
very mesomorphic


![](figures/198.2)


<!-- PageBreak -->

<!-- PageNumber: 165 -->


Nasser El Sonbaty, an endo-
mesomorph

![](figures/199.1)


