# REVERSE WRIST CURLS WITH DUMBBELLS

Reverse Curls work the forearm exten-
sors. Using dumbbells, you ensure that
each side of the body will work up to its
own capacity, with no help from the
other.


![](figures/507.1)


<!-- PageBreak -->

