The posedown helps the judges make their final decision, but it can
also be the most enjoyable part of the contest for the audience. It is like
watching Roman gladiators in hand-to-hand combat, only without the
swords and tridents. When the top bodybuilders in the world begin to duel
on a championship stage, the decibel reading in the auditorium goes right
off the scale-and the more enthusiastic the cheering of the audience, the
